taunts.text: A big cup of kicking your ass!
A big mug of my foot up your ass!
I love the smell of a kicked ass in the morning!
War is hell! Freedom isn't free! I am in a tank!
I will drive this tank up your ass, maggot!
I am about to tattoo some tank treads on your ass!
This is my tank! There are many like it, but this one is mine!
Wars may be fought with tanks, but they are won by men! With tanks!
Anything worth fighting for is worth fighting for in a tank!
War! What is it good for? Everything!
This tank runs on blood, guts, and glory! The guts and glory I will provide! The blood is where you come in!
This tank and the hero driving it, we're both made in America!
Sound off if you love freedom, maggot!
If you know what's good for ya, you will run!
You are scum! You are nothin' but a buncha' cowards!
If God had wanted you to live, He would not have created me!
Take your lumps like a man, Private Twinkletoes.
You are all weak. You are all bleeders.
Each and every one of you will be sent home to your momma' in a box!
We have you surrounded, at least from this side!
Do not look at me, I did not ask you a question!
Surrender now maggots and you will not be harmed!
You are a maggot hatched from a mutant maggot egg!
Look at you, maggot! Even your weapon needs a haircut!
You were loud and ugly and now you're DEAD! Amen.
You were good son, real good; maybe even the best.
You're a disgrace to the uniform.
If you know what's good for ya, you will run!
You are a maggot hatched from a mutant maggot egg!
Say your prayers and grab some air!
Ooh! Ah! Hah hah! Hoo hoo!
There's nothing more American than exercise!
I am having a heart attack!
Butt my head, that's an order!
He he he he he hah hah!
There are many like it, but this one is mine.
I'm not gonna just give it to ya. You'd like that, wouldn't you? Comrade...
I will trade this thing to you for another thing that you have.

Son, your hat is writing checks your head cannot cash!
That is not a hat, that is an excuse to kick your ass!
That is not a hat, that is proof that you hate America!
Do you call that a hat? That is a pile of nonsense!
Son, your fashion sense has gone AWOL!
That thing is not a weapon! That thing is why the enemy wins!
You do not skip around in this man's battlefield with a weapon like that!
Look at you, maggot! Even your weapon needs a haircut!
Do you call that a weapon, son? Somewhere, your father is weeping because of you!
